FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Well, commission or no commission, I ain't gonna starve.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~不论是否加入委员会，我都不能饿死。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Well, at least I don't have to see that weasel Dimitri in the flesh.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~算了，至少我不用跟那个奸诈的Dimitri见面。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I ain't come this far to lose that cash. Come on, Niko.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~事到如今怎么可能放手。跟上，Niko。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Alright, let's go back to the club.
~z~Dimitri can look after himself. See you later.
~z~I'm out. This was the last one. I'm taking my money and staying out of this shit.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我收手了，这是最后一票。拿到分成以后我就远离这行了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~He's out of it. Let's finish this thing.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~他不干了。让我们结束这件事。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Don't go too far, Niko. Follow me.
~z~When we get word that the brown is good, we'll give up the cash.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~等那边通知我们货物合格，我们就交钱。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~If I was you, I'd go and get the money off them. It has to be on the site.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~要我说，就去把他们的钱抢过来。钱肯定备好了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Thanks, Niko. I can't think of anyone else I woulda preferred to have with me in a spot like that.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~谢了Niko。当时有你在真是不幸中的万幸了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~If you thought that Ray was slippery, Dimitri is a different level.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~如果说Ray很狡猾的话，Dimitri是另一个境界。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Fuck, we gotta get him. I ain't going home empty handed from this. Dimitri would love that.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~操！我们要得到他。我不会空手而归。Dimitri会很喜欢这个。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~This is not going to stop us getting the money.
~z~He's waiting for you down in Tudor.
~z~Shit. We were so close. We did all that shit for nothing. I'll see you around man.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~妈的，就差一点。前面全他妈白干了。我们之后见，兄弟。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~That's a smart move. I worked with him and he double crossed me.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~明智之举。之前我跟他合作就被背叛了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Real? What the fuck is real? Real because it's you?
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~真的？什么他妈叫真的？关系到你就是真的？

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I heard that song before. Maybe it'll work out for you, good luck.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~这话我之前听过。也许你能做到，祝你好运。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~People don't want me around, they don't have to have me.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~他们不想让我加入，那就甭加入了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Fuck you - I looked out for you. And I'll pay good. Real good.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~操你妈，我罩过你。我会给个好价钱的，很好的价钱。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Hey, Phil. You excited about this deal?
~z~We've got legal problems, all kinds of crap.
~z~We're going back to the site, Niko.
~z~I don't care what falls in our path, we are getting the cash.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~什么挡路我无所谓，钱一定是我们的。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~He ain't someone I'd work with more than once, no matter how much he's earning us.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~这种人我不会跟他合作第二次，钱再多也不会。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~His own mother won't be able to recognize him when I'm done with him.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~看我不收拾得他连亲妈都认不出来。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~You always have to work for it.
~z~You didn't need to clip him, Niko. Shit.
~z~I nearly got killed and I never thought I'd cooperate with him again.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我差点没命，没想到现在又会跟他合作。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~He thinks this will hold us back.
~z~There ain't no try, we're getting him. Come on.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~没有什么是不能试试的，我们就要抓住他了，快来。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Shit, Phil. Anywhere'd be a better place than being in my shoes right now.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~妈的，Phil啊。随便哪里都比我现在的处境好。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Thank fucking God. That certainly wasn't simple.
~z~I should not have let you put me in the situation, Dimtri.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我本不应该你让把我陷入困境，Dimtri。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~You think you can get in this work for an easy buck but you end up in deep shit every time.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~你以为能轻轻松松赚大钱，结果每次都是一团糟。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~This is not going to stop us.
~z~I don't think anything is straight forward.
~z~I just wish I hadn't been put in that position.
~z~We've had to kill a lot of men for this money. It's rightfully ours.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我们为此被迫杀了一堆人，钱当然是我们的

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~If I don't got Phil, I don't got much. I'm screwed.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~要是没了Phil，我就没胜算了。我完了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I will not let you stand in my way.
~z~I guess he wanted it to be him and Pegorino.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我猜他想成为Pegorino和Dimitri那样的人。   //没太看懂啥意思

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~At least you knew what Ray was after from day one, Dimitri can turn on his best friend in a second.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~至少一见到Ray就能看穿他的本性，Dimitri随时可以跟他的挚友翻脸。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Dimitri's giving the buyer the H while we pick up the money.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~Dimitri会把白粉交给买家，我们负责收钱。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~The cash is what we're after, not your lives.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我们的追求是钱，不是你的命。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~He's crashed. Go get the money, Niko.
~z~Dimtri did not give us a choice about this.
~z~Oh, he is not going anywhere. Not with our money.
~z~Fucking Dimitri, he's killed the guys collecting the stuff.
~z~So, why are you working with him again?
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~所以，为什么你要再次和他合作？

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~The punk is getting away with the money. I ain't come this far to let it go. Come on.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~那个混帐想带着钱走人。事到如今他还想跑？快追。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~And I'll pay a lot of money.
~z~Up on the roof, Niko. Let's see if we can figure out what's going on inside.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~先上房顶，Niko。看看能不能看见内部情况。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Let's fucking disappoint him. We're coming back alive and with the money. Come on.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我们搞他一下。我们会带着钱活着回来。加油。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Dimitri would love it if we didn't come back at all.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~如果我们根本就不会来，Dimitri 会喜欢这样的。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I came here for that money, I am leaving with it.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我来这里是为了钱，我要带它走。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~How come everything we get into starts off simple and ends up real complicated?
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我们那些开头简单的活好像没一个结尾不难的吧。
~z~Dimtri是个表面一套，背后一套的人。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Something didn't look right about him. I don't know, there was something in his eyes.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~他这人看上去是不太对。说不清楚，看不透他的想法。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Alright there, Phil. Seen any choppers or submarines or anything?
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~好了，Phil。有看见什么上天入地的特工吗？

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Keep safe and enjoy the money. Ciao.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~注意安全，享用这笔钱吧。再见。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~They're gonna be coming after us so we may as well make a play for the money while we still got a jump on 'em.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~他们会追杀我们的，最好还是趁着还能突袭的时候为钱搏一把。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~What the fuck are you doing? These boys ain't gonna do business with us now.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~你他妈的在干嘛？这些人现在不会和我们交易了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We know you have that money here.
~z~Where is he going with our money?
~z~The whole operation isn't professional. He'll understand.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~整个行动太不专业了。他懂的。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Yeah, I met him when Jimmy P set up the deal. There's something about him I don't trust.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~嗯，Jimmy P安排这次交易的时候我见过他。我不太信任这个人。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We're going to Port Tudor. Let's move.
~z~This is just a straightforward money pickup. Dimitri is gonna hand over the H on his end.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~这次就是个简单的收钱工作。Dimitri那边拿白粉交货，

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Niko, I can't get in. You gotta give me some help.
~z~You think these fucking scumbags are gonna let us leave after this? Fuck.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~你觉得这群混蛋还会放我们走吗？操。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~At least we got the cash. That's the one thing we can bring away from this fucked up situation.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~至少我们拿到钱了。这种情况下唯一能得到的收获。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I just want to take the money and go home.
~z~I want to get this money and go home.
~z~Niko Bellic, it's so good to be working with you again.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~Niko Bellic，和你再次合作真是太好了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I guess you get used to it when you hang around him long enough.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~跟他合作多了大概就习惯了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Fucking Dimitri. I ain't never been put in a situation like that before.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~狗逼Dimitri。我还真没见过这种场面。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Come on, let me take the money or you will die.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~快点，让我带走这笔钱否则我杀了你。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We got the jump on them right now. Follow me.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~现在就向他们发起突袭，跟我来。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Alright, the money's in there. Once we're in, it's all or nothing.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~好了，钱就在里面。这次进去，就是背水一战。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Mr. Pegorino. Phil didn't make it. He's in a better place.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~ Pegorino先生。Phil挂了。他现在在一个更好的地方。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I thought it'd be easier if I just killed those guys and kept it.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~直接杀了他们把货留着好像更容易些。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Alright, Niko. You go that way, I'll go this way. We'll close 'em in.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~好的，Niko。你走那条路，我走这条路。这样我们会接近他们。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We are getting the cash off him. Be sure of that.
~z~We got to get that money, Phil.
~z~I know... but this is real. I need you.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我知道...但这次是真的。我需要你。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Yo, that's the guy with the cash.
~z~Sometimes it ain't worth sacrificing a pay check for personal differences.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~有时为了点个人恩怨就放弃赚钱不值得。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Alright, if we're fighting, we're fighting for the money.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~好吧，就算要战，那也是为钱而战。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Had you learnt that then you wouldn't be sitting pretty on a load of green right now, would you?
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~早明白的话，你现在还能坐拥一堆绿票子吗？

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~No, you listen, you dumb immigrant fuck. I ain't asking you. I'm telling you. Do this!
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~不，你听着，白痴移民崽子。我不是在求你，这是命令，你照做！

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Dimitri likes to set up executions. He set up his best friend Mikhail Faustin.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~Dimitri最喜欢送人上那儿。他最好的朋友Mikhail Faustin就被送上去了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~This is it, Phil. Let's get the cash.
~z~I cannot say I have the same enthusiasm for this partnership. Have you given them the H?
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~这次合作我反正是没你这么高兴。白粉你交出去了吗？

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~He killed the guys instead of handing over the H. We should get out of here.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~他杀了负责收货的人，没交付白粉。我们该跑了

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I looked out for you, you know. People wanted to whack you, I said no.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我罩过你，要知道。之前有人想杀你，我不同意。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~If they'd gotten tipped off before Dimitri called us, we woulda been fucked.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~要是他们在Dimitri打电话之前就收到了消息，我们早完了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Look, Phil will look after you. You won't even have to deal with the fucking Russians.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~听着，Phil会跟你一起去。你都不用跟那些混蛋俄国佬见面。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Listen, Mr. Pegorino. I already told you. I got history...
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~听着，Pegorino先生。我都说过了，我跟他有...

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We'll get a call from him when they have the stuff, then the buyers will hand over the funds.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~货物交付以后他会联系我们，然后买家给我们结帐。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Shit, we're screwed. They ain't gonna let us leave.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~妈的，我们麻烦了。他们不会放我们走的。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Now I got the money and I'm going to forget all about this shit.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~现在钱到手了，这些破事就都忘了吧。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~That's true Phil. It's never fucking easy, is it? You can't just walk in somewhere and get free money.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~确实如此，Phil。从来都不简单，对吗？天上不会掉馅饼。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Hell, Niko. That just weren't professional. I gotta explain this to Jimmy.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~糟了，Niko。这太不专业了。我得向Jimmy解释。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Especially when you've got a snake like Dimitri Rascalov working with you.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~特别是跟Dimitri Rascalov这种小人合作的时候。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I'm not leaving here without a payday, Phil.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~今天没有收获，我不会离开这里，Phil。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~What's going to happen when they find out?
~z~Do it - or you and me are gonna have a problem.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~去吧，不然我让你吃不了兜着走。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I knew I could count on you.
~z~I learnt a lesson. I learnt that people don't change.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我明白了一件事，江山易改本性难移。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Hey, are you guys here to pick up the cash?
~z~No, it's over for me, I'm out. If I was going to kill him I would have done that instead of this deal.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~不，与我无关了，我收手了。要杀他的话我早去了，哪会过来交易。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Where is the cash? Give it to us.
~z~You get close to your dream, then something holds you back.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~你离梦想一步之遥，却被拽了回去。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We're in this together man, come on, come on.
~z~No. I need you to get that H. I need the money.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~不，我需要你去拿白粉，我需要钱。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Then we're gonna get a call saying we're good to go.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~接到他的通知我们就去收钱。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Get over your principles, these guys don't hold grudges.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~放弃你的原则吧，这些人不记仇的。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Money makes people do the strangest things, don't it?
~z~I'll do my best, we'll try and catch him.
~z~You know what? I thought, 'Why should we hand over the H for this price?'
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~说实话，我觉得吧，「这价钱把粉交出去不是贱卖吗？」

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Fucking Dimitri, that spineless shit. He's fucked us.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~狗逼Dimitri，没骨气的玩意儿。他耍了我们。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~That way we all win. Good luck, Niko.
~z~You just head into the compound and wait for us to give you the nod.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~你把车开进厂区，等我们的消息就行。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I am going to think about Dimitri when we kill this man with our money.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~把钱抢回来后我会考虑Dimitri的事的。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~If they going to fuck you over once they'll fuck you again. Wish I realized that before.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~一朝蛇咬你，十年蛇咬你。真希望我能早点明白。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~But I need you to do something.
~z~I did not kill those men to have this stuff stop me getting the cash.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我都杀到这儿了，哪会让这种东西阻止我拿钱。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We need to catch this car, Niko. I been fucked around enough and I ain't walking away with nothing.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~我们要追上那辆车，Niko。我已经被操的遍体鳞伤了，我不会空着手离开。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~They'll hand over the cash and we're out of there.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~他们把钱一给，我们就能走了。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~We need a car if we're gonna chase that bastard.
~z~Easier for who? What the fuck are you doing? Me and Phil are in their compound.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~谁简单啊？你他妈在干啥？我和Phil还在他们的地盘。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Get after him. Come on, Niko. Get that motherfucker.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~追上去，快点，干死那个狗娘养的。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Sold me out to someone I had history with.
~z~We are going to get that money, Phil.
~z~I need you to collect that H, I got some Russians who have a buyer.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~需要你拿上那些H，我联络到俄国人了，他们有下家。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~I need you to lay down some covering fire.
~z~I hate to think what's gone down on Dimitri's end. I'm calling Jimmy.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~都不敢想Dimitri那边会怎么样。我给Jimmy打个电话。

FIN1AAU.original: ~z~Good luck to you, man. I hope it works out.
FIN1AAU.translated: ~z~祝你好运，兄弟，希望如你所愿。
